data.description: Previous contract terminated due to buyer's financing. This quaint, cosmetically updated home on more than an acre in Summertown has the privacy that you've been looking for! Just 1,000 feet from the Buffalo River, this property allows access to the river amenities in the Buffalo Run Estates subdivision, with NO HOA! Your 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home backs up entirely to green space with only one neighbor across the driveway. Summertown/Ethridge is home to the Amish community. Every road to this property is a beautiful drive. See it for yourself today! Sellers are willing to negotiate an interest rate buy-down due to rising rates. This property qualifies for 0% down USDA financing! Listing Agent is providing a full coverage home warranty for this property, ordered by Benchmark Realty, LLC.
